    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduo a Sphinxcontrib-htmlhelp Module</title>

      <para>
        The <application>Sphinxcontrib-htmlhelp</application> package is a
<application>Sphinx</application> extension which renders HTML help files.
      </para>

      &lfs113_checked;

